                <label class="kg4">__________________</label>
                <label class="kg5">__________________</label>
                <div class="dimension"> </div>
                <h6 class="card-header bold routingtxt">Routing Information :</h6>
                <hr class="hrline2" />
                <p class="pclass">Airline Carrier :</p>
                <label class="carrier">_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________</label>
                <p class="pclass" style="margin: -55px 181px;">Airline Carrier</p>
                <br /><br />
                <br /><br />
                <p>
                    Breakdown: WEIGHT :
                    AIR FREIGHT [45.00MIN / per KG] :
                    FUEL [INCLUDED] :
                    SECURITY [INCLUDED] :
